one christmas is a 1994 american made-for-television drama film starring katharine hepburn ( in her final film role ) , henry winkler and swoosie kurtz . it is based on the 1983 short story " one christmas " by truman capote about a young boy who reluctantly leaves his alabama home to spend christmas with his estranged father in new orleans . the film originally premiered on nbc on december 19 , 1994 .